This luxe hotel in a high-rise is a 4-minute walk from Vancouver City Centre Station's SkyTrain's and shopping at the Pacific Centre Mall.

description:
Situated within walking distance of the centre of Jasper,  the Jewel of the Rockies, Bjorn's Beds offers a quiet resting place from the demands of exploring one of Canada's most beautiful National Parks.

With a private entrance to the guest area, visitors have the choice of two rooms.  One room has a private bathroom with a shower. The second bathroom is adjacent to the sitting area, and contains bathtub and shower. The rooms are bright, clean and spacious with dresser, closet and a queen size bed.  Wireless internet and television available.

description:
Set in Scanno, B&B Angela offers a garden, terrace and classic-style accommodation with a TV. Free WiFi is available in public areas.

Rooms at the Angela all come with a desk and private bathroom with a hairdryer and free toiletries.

A sweet Italian buffet breakfast is served daily, while savoury items are available on request.

address: 1580 Montee du Cure Labelle Mont Tremblant Quebec
description:
This secluded resort on 200 acres of woodland caters specifically for guests with dogs. The town of Mont-Tremblant is 6.8 km, and Parc national du Mont-Tremblant is 66.7 km away.


Cozy rooms are furnished in a rustic style with pine-clad walls and fully equipped kitchens (some with dishwashers and washer/dryers). All rooms come with satellite TV, free WiFi, fireplaces and barbecues.

Facilities include a private lake, free use of canoes and pedal boats, and walking trails. Homemade ready-to-cook meals can be provided for an extra charge. Amenities for dogs include day camp, grooming, boarding and private walks.
